    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It is mechanically sound and performs reliably. There is some minor cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior from normal use. All major systems are operational.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining in the footwells. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it will likely need suspension work and a new set of tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine requires significant repair to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is visible rust on the body panels and the paint has faded significantly, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including several tears in the upholstery. It will likely need to be towed from its current location, but it offers a solid foundation for a dedicated restoration project.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is ready for a fresh start and represents a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to take on a full restoration project. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's the perfect affordable entry point for a dedicated builder to bring a classic back to life!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this well-maintained vehicle, characterized by its mechanical integrity and consistent performance. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our standards for safety and operational excellence. The exterior retains a professional finish, while the interior remains refined and orderly. This offering represents a premier opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle at a competitive market valuation.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly such a great find for anyone looking for a reliable ride. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been super dependable for all my errands and weekend trips. It drives smoothly, looks great, and I\u2019ve really stayed on top of keeping it clean and happy. If you're looking for a solid vehicle that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L straight-six features individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and sent to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal traction. The chassis has been vetted for subframe integrity, and the suspension retains its signature damping characteristics. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system refresh, ensuring the thermal efficiency of the iron-block engine. This is a driver-focused machine with sharp throttle response and balanced weight distribution, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. Minor exterior wear.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior finish retains a deep, impressive gloss, with only the minor, unavoidable stone chips one expects from careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of any significant wear, while the dashboard and trim pieces are in excellent shape. Mechanically, this car is top-tier for its class. It has benefited from a rigorous maintenance schedule, resulting in a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that starts reliably every time. All onboard electronics, from the infotainment system to the climate control, function perfectly. Whether you are looking for a dependable commuter or a stylish weekend cruiser, this car offers a refined driving experience and the peace of mind that comes from a history of responsible ownership.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and refined performance. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Boasting a sophisticated profile and a consistent service history, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    }
